name: Digital Only Sharps Sunglasses
description: These sunglasses are modeled by Martina Ponzoni from the archive of designer Shayli Harrisonâ€™s Sharps collection, which was inspired by a subculture known as Sharpies or Sharps that emerged out of Australia during the late sixties.
